oc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Tong_quan_cach_choi_bai_ma_soi_Trung_Quoc\" >T\u1ed5ng quan c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Huong_dan_cach_choi_bai_ma_soi_Trung_Quoc\" >H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Buoc_chuan_bi_truoc_khi_choi_ma_soi\" >B\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u01a1i ma s\u00f3i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Vai_tro_noi_bat_doi_voi_cac_nhan_vat\" >Vai tr\u00f2 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Cac_giai_doan_va_cach_xac_dinh_nguoi_chien_thang\" >C\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Giai_doan_vao_ban_dem\" >Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Giai_doan_vao_thoi_diem_ban_dem\" >Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ban \u0111\u00eam<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc\/\">C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/a> \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng suy lu\u1eadn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 danh t\u00ednh th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">Sv368<\/a> s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn anh em th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn game n\u00e0y!<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tong_quan_cach_choi_bai_ma_soi_Trung_Quoc\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ma s\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadp vai, suy lu\u1eadn n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh hai phe: phe ma s\u00f3i v\u00e0 d\u00e2n l\u00e0ng. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o h\u00e0nh vi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch giao ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 phe d\u00e2n l\u00e0ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ma s\u00f3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, phe ma s\u00f3i ph\u1ea3i che gi\u1ea5u th\u00e2n ph\u1eadn v\u00e0 ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt kh\u00e1c. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i qua hai giai \u0111o\u1ea1n, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed gay c\u1ea5n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fa v\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb 6 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u00ean, khi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn\u00a0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c. V\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp vai v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cao, ma s\u00f3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai y\u00eau th\u00edch suy lu\u1eadn.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5013\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5013\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5013 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-1.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-1.jpg?v=1736648988 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-1-300x150.jpg?v=1736648988 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-1-768x384.jpg?v=1736648988 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5013\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng quan c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_cach_choi_bai_ma_soi_Trung_Quoc\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi hay mu\u1ed1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 game n\u00e0y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_chuan_bi_truoc_khi_choi_ma_soi\"><\/span><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u01a1i ma s\u00f3i<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c th\u1ebb nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt. Ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i. Qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n ph\u00e1t ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c th\u1ebb nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt cho t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1eefng vai tr\u00f2 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n bao g\u1ed3m d\u00e2n l\u00e0ng, ma s\u00f3i hay m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 ph\u00f9 th\u1ee7y, ti\u00ean tri ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Anh em n\u00ean ng\u1ed3i th\u00e0nh v\u00f2ng tr\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c giao ti\u1ebfp. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i di\u1ec5n ra, qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn v\u1ec1 lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch tham gia gi\u00fap m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5014\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5014\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5014 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-2.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-2.jpg?v=1736649015 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-2-300x150.jpg?v=1736649015 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-2-768x384.jpg?v=1736649015 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5014\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u01a1i ma s\u00f3i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vai_tro_noi_bat_doi_voi_cac_nhan_vat\"><\/span><b>Vai tr\u00f2 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed7i nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt trong ma s\u00f3i \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c phe c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0m cho tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c vai tr\u00f2 ch\u00ednh trong <strong>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/strong>:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ma s\u00f3i:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 phe \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp v\u1edbi d\u00e2n l\u00e0ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a soi l\u00e0 ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c phe m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi che gi\u1ea5u danh t\u00ednh. M\u1ed7i \u0111\u00eam, ma s\u00f3i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng nhau th\u1ee9c d\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>D\u00e2n l\u00e0ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Phe n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng suy lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u00f3i v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ti\u00ean tri:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng soi danh t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i m\u1ed7i \u0111\u00eam. Th\u00f4ng tin thu nh\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap ti\u00ean tri h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn d\u00e2n l\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ma s\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ph\u00f9 Th\u1ee7y:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Trong <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu hai lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c: c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a s\u00f3i v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n trong su\u1ed1t tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u00f9 th\u1ee7y c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng khi ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i kh\u1ecfi b\u1ecb s\u00f3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trong \u0111\u00eam. N\u1ebfu s\u00f3i ch\u1ecdn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd an to\u00e0n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee9u c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong hai \u0111\u00eam li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5015\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5015\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5015 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-3.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-3.jpg?v=1736649049 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-3-300x150.jpg?v=1736649049 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-3-768x384.jpg?v=1736649049 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5015\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_giai_doan_va_cach_xac_dinh_nguoi_chien_thang\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh hai giai \u0111o\u1ea1n lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean: \u0111\u00eam v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giai_doan_vao_ban_dem\"><\/span><b>Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u00eam, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1ecdi t\u1eebng vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ee9c d\u1eady theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ma s\u00f3i:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> S\u00f3i th\u1ee9c d\u1eady \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ra d\u1ea5u v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ti\u00ean tri:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Sau \u0111\u00f3, ti\u00ean tri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 h\u1ecfi qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 xem ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ma s\u00f3i hay d\u00e2n l\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ph\u00f9 th\u1ee7y:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Ti\u1ebfp theo, ph\u00f9 th\u1ee7y th\u1ee9c d\u1eady v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c c\u1ee9u n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb ma s\u00f3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giai_doan_vao_thoi_diem_ban_dem\"><\/span><b>Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ban \u0111\u00eam<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, khi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ng\u00e0y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf m\u1eaft v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o danh t\u00ednh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ma s\u00f3i trong ban \u0111\u00eam. Ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n tranh lu\u1eadn, n\u01a1i m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 danh t\u00ednh th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi tranh lu\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac, c\u1ea3 nh\u00f3m s\u1ebd b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nghi ng\u1edd l\u00e0 ma s\u00f3i v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf kh\u1ecfi tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n n\u00f3i l\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng ch\u01a1i. Chu k\u1ef3 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00eam v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5016\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5016\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5016 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-4.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-4.jpg?v=1736649076 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-4-300x150.jpg?v=1736649076 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-bai-ma-soi-trung-quoc-4-768x384.jpg?v=1736649076 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5016\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn anh em nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. N\u1eafm v\u1eefng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i, lu\u1eadt c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n, h\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i Sv368 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i ma s\u00f3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng suy lu\u1eadn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 danh t\u00ednh th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Sv368 s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn anh em th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5014,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},